snippet.title: Firefight Preview
snippet.description:
To get this game for Windows, iOS or Android go to: http://www.windowsgames.co.uk/ff.html

Preview of my game "Firefight" - available on Steam, the iOS AppStore, Google Store and Windows Store. All of the clips are from actual in-game play.
